{"tid":458522,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"日式火鍋放題 咩湯底係必叫 ?","createTime":"2017-11-05T02:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T09:00:11.000Z","uid":29093,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5159f9c589f4031f9a7c803a4f3cfc4007fff278","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"日式火鍋放題 咩湯底係必叫 ?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n<br />\n係咪 壽喜燒 最穩陣 ? <br />\n<br />\n咩牛乳好似肯定好撚淡味"},{"pid":"dad8273f2ff4c3505346bf5d6241a114b24a1a19","tid":458522,"uid":9284,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"全部垃圾  牛刷鍋 牛乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉野家濃湯仲好食過佢"},{"pid":"ccedd96f01186e6ed1979678f7d4e34c27ff9196","tid":458522,"uid":139613,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"重慶麻辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c342aa2fca1f5050970fc8c58c519d9e2d34a785","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部垃圾  牛刷鍋 牛乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉野家濃湯仲好食過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間唔中,  半年食一次 日式火鍋放題 都 ok 既 ,  多野食嘛 <br />\n<br />\n但火鍋最重要既就係湯底,  做錯決定就成餐飯都唔撚駛食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n吉野家濃湯 好似係咩 昆布 + 味林  + 日式醬油 ?"},{"pid":"4f8af37fff962dc07c63a458596fe10e34f69a4f","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重慶麻辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有得揀兩款湯底,  我都想揀麻辣 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   打邊爐就係要重口味架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee95c46c342594fa2cdd88bba159b0971e1f9f38","tid":458522,"uid":67060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全部垃圾  牛刷鍋 牛乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吉野家濃湯仲好食過佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間唔中,  半年食一次 日式火鍋放題 都 ok 既 ,  多野食嘛 <br />\n<br />\n但火鍋最重要既就係湯底,  做錯決定就成餐飯都唔撚駛食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n吉野家濃湯 好似係咩 昆布 + 味林  + 日式醬油 ?</blockquote><br />\n打邊爐最重要係個爐啊"},{"pid":"eea2d6612ef498279a7761cb7ee869bb65416559","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"龍蝦湯嗰啲 好似伏伏地 ?"},{"pid":"18358b1c9407040bebe6d8a4ce45fab156c738a5","tid":458522,"uid":80176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"豆乳<br />\n抹茶"},{"pid":"b6138f1b9de03b70e1cf0731d80d335f54c914af","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豆乳<br />\n抹茶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果間野未食過,  叫豆乳好驚中大伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2744fec88848e5a149ed6409ff142c32a5c754","tid":458522,"uid":11977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"除左壽喜/昆布<br />\n其他煲煲下都好多泡"},{"pid":"e94c3db5c8156afc815a78be236bfd4517402938","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左壽喜/昆布<br />\n其他煲煲下都好多泡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉,  其實啲泡點嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af201d52d93c2f1a8ee0666128e10037635039b","tid":458522,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人叫慣昆布湯講下,  食落同吉野家濃湯爭幾遠 ?   <br />\n<br />\n係咪吉野家濃湯 重口味啲 ?"},{"pid":"face3dc22b153520b3a81b2cd6592d05d99e493f","tid":4